WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:04.000
{\an8}<b><font color="#9CD5FF">One Pace Premium</font></b>
Keep the project alive: <font color="#a8c7fa">ko-fi.com/not6ip</font>

2
00:01:55.800 --> 00:02:01.180
Express to the Main Island
of Enies Lobby

3
00:02:07.110 --> 00:02:09.780
It's been a while, Chief.

4
00:02:13.240 --> 00:02:19.120
Eight years ago, he assaulted
government officials in Water Seven:

5
00:02:19.120 --> 00:02:21.120
the fugitive Cutty Flam.

6
00:02:21.120 --> 00:02:27.590
And the criminal responsible for an attack
on Marine battleships at Ohara in the West Blue:

7
00:02:27.590 --> 00:02:29.170
Nico Robin.

8
00:02:29.170 --> 00:02:32.010
We've brought them here without a hitch.

9
00:02:32.720 --> 00:02:35.090
Both are behind those doors.

10
00:02:36.090 --> 00:02:37.550
Welcome back,

11
00:02:37.890 --> 00:02:41.640
Lucci, Kaku, Blueno, and Kalifa!

12
00:02:41.640 --> 00:02:42.930
That's sexual harassment.

13
00:02:42.930 --> 00:02:44.890
Just from saying your name?!

14
00:02:48.860 --> 00:02:51.610
Long time no see, Lucci.

15
00:02:51.610 --> 00:02:54.650
I see you look more arrogant than ever.

16
00:02:55.110 --> 00:02:58.070
And I see you look dumber than ever, Jabra.

17
00:02:58.740 --> 00:03:00.490
What'd you say?

18
00:03:01.540 --> 00:03:03.580
Hold your horses.

19
00:03:03.580 --> 00:03:05.790
We just got back.

20
00:03:07.460 --> 00:03:11.920
He is correct. The two of you
must desist at once!

21
00:03:12.800 --> 00:03:19.970
After all, this is a reunion
five years in the making!

22
00:03:39.530 --> 00:03:40.160
Ow...!

23
00:03:41.620 --> 00:03:44.950
Leave it to Fukuro to test us right away.

24
00:03:45.830 --> 00:03:48.790
Six Powers: Assessment!

25
00:03:49.380 --> 00:03:53.960
Suppose an armed guard
has a power level of ten.

26
00:03:51.500 --> 00:03:54.960
Power Level 10

27
00:03:53.960 --> 00:03:55.840
I will now reveal...

28
00:03:54.960 --> 00:03:55.090
Power Level 10

29
00:03:55.090 --> 00:03:55.210
Power Level 10

30
00:03:55.210 --> 00:03:55.840
Power Level 10

31
00:03:56.260 --> 00:03:58.630
your power levels.

32
00:03:58.630 --> 00:04:00.720
I will uncover your strengths.

33
00:04:00.720 --> 00:04:04.020
First, Kalifa: Power level 630.

34
00:04:04.020 --> 00:04:06.850
Blueno: Power level 820.

35
00:04:06.850 --> 00:04:09.770
Kaku: Power level 2,200.

36
00:04:10.100 --> 00:04:11.980
Lucci...

37
00:04:15.280 --> 00:04:16.940
Power level 4,000!

38
00:04:16.940 --> 00:04:20.110
You said 4,000?! Hey,
did you measure it properly?!

39
00:04:20.110 --> 00:04:22.370
No one has a power level that high!

40
00:04:22.370 --> 00:04:23.870
It's correct!

41
00:04:23.870 --> 00:04:26.080
Everyone got stronger!

42
00:04:28.290 --> 00:04:33.540
I already measured Jabra's and Kumadori's,
so now I know how we rank among ourselves.

43
00:04:39.340 --> 00:04:41.260
Hey, Fukuro! Objection!

44
00:04:41.640 --> 00:04:45.520
Lucci's one thing, but how the hell
am I weaker than Kaku?!

45
00:04:47.020 --> 00:04:49.690
Kaku got stronger too!

46
00:04:50.310 --> 00:04:53.520
Hey, don't let it go to your head, Kaku!

47
00:04:53.520 --> 00:04:56.650
The assessment skill just
measures raw strength.

48
00:04:57.240 --> 00:05:00.490
In an actual fight,
I'd also have devil fruit powers.

49
00:05:00.490 --> 00:05:03.370
Don't go thinking you could ever beat me!

50
00:05:03.370 --> 00:05:05.120
Think whatever you like.

51
00:05:05.120 --> 00:05:08.000
I don't give a rat's ass about that stuff.

52
00:05:08.000 --> 00:05:09.500
Well said.

53
00:05:09.500 --> 00:05:12.080
Don't lend your ears to a stray dog.

54
00:05:13.460 --> 00:05:18.550
What do you mean, "stray dog," Lucci?!
You mangy monster cat!

55
00:05:26.850 --> 00:05:29.230
Hey, stop it, both of you!

56
00:05:29.230 --> 00:05:33.810
Is it just me, or is Jabra
a bit touchier than usual?

57
00:05:33.810 --> 00:05:36.270
Every guard on the island is talking about

58
00:05:36.270 --> 00:05:41.490
how Jabra got rejected
by the waitress Gatherine yesterday.

59
00:05:41.490 --> 00:05:42.860
That explains it.

60
00:05:42.860 --> 00:05:44.570
H-Hey, hold on a sec!

61
00:05:44.570 --> 00:05:46.950
How does everyone know about that?!

62
00:05:46.950 --> 00:05:50.040
I blabbed about it to the guards
on the main island.

63
00:05:51.710 --> 00:05:52.920
It was you!

64
00:05:54.540 --> 00:05:56.880
Gatherine

65
00:05:56.880 --> 00:06:02.170
Oh, please! This is only an issue because you
started with all that ranking nonsense!

66
00:06:02.170 --> 00:06:08.890
Having mastered the Six Powers,
you have all far surpassed ordinary people.

67
00:06:08.890 --> 00:06:12.100
Isn't a power level of 500 enough
to give you superhuman status?

68
00:06:13.190 --> 00:06:16.560
Chief: Power level nine.
Less than one armed guard.

69
00:06:17.610 --> 00:06:20.990
Zip it, you! As your chief,
it shouldn't matter anyway!

70
00:06:20.990 --> 00:06:24.320
Besides, did you forget
about my special sword?!

71
00:06:24.320 --> 00:06:27.450
I've always known that you've
lacked certain attributes, Chief.

72
00:06:28.660 --> 00:06:33.370
H-H-H-Hey! You shouldn't be so blunt, Kalifa.

73
00:06:33.370 --> 00:06:34.460
That's sexual harassment.

74
00:06:34.460 --> 00:06:36.920
What?! Just by responding?!

75
00:06:38.590 --> 00:06:39.300
Chief...

76
00:06:39.300 --> 00:06:41.340
Wh-What is it?

77
00:06:41.760 --> 00:06:43.550
That's sexual harassment!

78
00:06:43.550 --> 00:06:44.550
Just existing?!

79
00:06:46.510 --> 00:06:50.470
Kalifa! How rude of you!

80
00:06:51.350 --> 00:06:58.060
Chief! A-Allow me to take responsibility
and commit ritual suicide immediately!

81
00:06:58.060 --> 00:06:59.690
Seppuku!

82
00:06:59.690 --> 00:07:00.900
Iron Body.

83
00:07:01.860 --> 00:07:05.610
For shame... I cannot die.

84
00:07:05.610 --> 00:07:07.820
Hurry up and die already!

85
00:07:08.490 --> 00:07:14.580
Anyway, you all performed spectacularly
over the past five years.

86
00:07:15.080 --> 00:07:16.330
Oh, I almost forgot.

87
00:07:16.330 --> 00:07:19.420
This isn't really a reward
for your efforts or anything,

88
00:07:19.420 --> 00:07:21.590
but I do have something I want to give you.

89
00:07:22.090 --> 00:07:25.090
Well, I'll do that later.

90
00:07:26.050 --> 00:07:28.090
In any case, I'd like to meet...

91
00:07:29.350 --> 00:07:31.850
the "hope" of the entire world!

92
00:07:43.320 --> 00:07:44.690
Go in already!

93
00:07:47.410 --> 00:07:48.820
You too!

94
00:08:01.670 --> 00:08:03.460
I'm just so excited!

95
00:08:03.920 --> 00:08:07.930
I'm surprised to see you survived
that accident eight years ago,

96
00:08:08.340 --> 00:08:09.930
Cutty Flam.

97
00:08:09.930 --> 00:08:11.430
There's also...

98
00:08:11.430 --> 00:08:15.180
one of the world's most dangerous,
most wanted women:

99
00:08:15.600 --> 00:08:17.230
Nico Robin!

100
00:08:17.940 --> 00:08:20.560
I feel fantastic! However...

101
00:08:20.560 --> 00:08:23.190
it's unfortunate that
the world's citizens don't know

102
00:08:23.190 --> 00:08:27.320
about the true value and magnitude
of the work accomplished today.

103
00:08:27.320 --> 00:08:29.320
It'll be several years...

104
00:08:30.320 --> 00:08:34.490
before anything about today
even comes to light.

105
00:08:35.660 --> 00:08:40.790
I believe the justice doled out by those
old government geezers is too lenient!

106
00:08:41.130 --> 00:08:44.130
Only through sacrifice
will we achieve our goal.

107
00:08:44.840 --> 00:08:48.510
Our hard work will ensure peace
for all of humanity.

108
00:08:49.970 --> 00:08:57.100
Killing some of the fools standing in our way
is a small sacrifice for world peace.

109
00:08:57.430 --> 00:09:02.270
Fools like that fishman, who refused
to hand over a certain something.

110
00:09:02.270 --> 00:09:07.070
As a rebel against justice,
of course he deserved death.

111
00:09:10.740 --> 00:09:12.990
He definitely deserved it!

112
00:09:14.530 --> 00:09:16.120
You're insane!

113
00:09:16.120 --> 00:09:18.870
Mr. Tom lost his life
protecting those blueprints!

114
00:09:19.290 --> 00:09:22.500
He died because of idiots like you!

115
00:09:27.420 --> 00:09:31.010
Wh-What're you doing?!
Help me, guys! Hey!

116
00:09:32.430 --> 00:09:35.350
Ow, ow! Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow! Ow!

117
00:09:35.680 --> 00:09:37.390
Kumadori!

118
00:09:40.020 --> 00:09:43.980
Roger!

119
00:09:44.400 --> 00:09:46.770
Hurry up and help me, hey! Hey!

120
00:09:47.440 --> 00:09:50.900
Now... now... now...!

121
00:10:10.170 --> 00:10:11.800
Gum-Gum...

122
00:10:11.800 --> 00:10:14.010
Gatling!

123
00:10:14.010 --> 00:10:15.390
Gum-Gum...

124
00:10:15.390 --> 00:10:17.810
Whip!

125
00:10:20.180 --> 00:10:21.930
Giant Scythe!

126
00:10:24.230 --> 00:10:25.770
Bell!

127
00:10:27.230 --> 00:10:29.150
Mallet!

128
00:10:30.650 --> 00:10:32.780
Bazooka!

129
00:10:38.530 --> 00:10:39.950
Gum-Gum...

130
00:10:39.950 --> 00:10:40.910
Stamp!

131
00:10:44.420 --> 00:10:46.290
Chief, main island reporting!

132
00:10:46.290 --> 00:10:49.460
Chief Spandam! Please respond!

133
00:10:49.960 --> 00:10:51.550
It's no use! I can't get through!

134
00:10:51.550 --> 00:10:54.220
Is his receiver off the hook again...?

135
00:10:54.220 --> 00:10:55.680
Not now!

136
00:10:55.680 --> 00:10:58.390
Seriously, not at a critical time like this!

137
00:10:58.890 --> 00:11:01.350
Hey, where did Straw Hat go?

138
00:11:01.350 --> 00:11:03.060
He's right beneath you!

139
00:11:03.060 --> 00:11:04.940
What?! Right beneath us?!

140
00:11:07.690 --> 00:11:09.690
Get him already!

141
00:11:10.270 --> 00:11:11.570
There! Down there!

142
00:11:11.570 --> 00:11:12.900
Dammit! Boxed in!

143
00:11:20.370 --> 00:11:22.700
Gum-Gum...

144
00:11:22.700 --> 00:11:24.960
Volcano!

145
00:11:49.980 --> 00:11:53.900
Th... The wall...! The wall is falling!

146
00:11:54.940 --> 00:11:56.320
Get clear!

147
00:11:59.450 --> 00:12:02.240
Gum-Gum...

148
00:12:02.910 --> 00:12:06.370
Gatling!

149
00:12:07.250 --> 00:12:08.580
Watch out!

150
00:12:13.630 --> 00:12:16.090
Chief Spandam! Please come in!

151
00:12:16.090 --> 00:12:19.890
We need a plan of action!
We can't stop Straw Hat Luffy!

152
00:12:21.100 --> 00:12:24.010
Straw Hat Luffy is headed to the courthouse!

153
00:12:21.140 --> 00:12:25.890
Courthouse, Main Island
Enies Lobby

154
00:12:24.010 --> 00:12:25.890
Tighten our defenses! On the double!

155
00:12:25.890 --> 00:12:27.600
Be quiet!

156
00:12:27.600 --> 00:12:29.140
What's this ruckus?!

157
00:12:29.140 --> 00:12:31.810
You woke me up!

158
00:12:31.810 --> 00:12:33.730
Ch-Chief Justice!

159
00:12:34.780 --> 00:12:35.780
"Three-Headed" Baskerville
Chief Justice, Enies Lobby

