344
00:15:27.490 --> 00:15:28.530
Hey...

345
00:15:32.160 --> 00:15:34.790
Is that... a sea train?

346
00:15:34.790 --> 00:15:36.250
What's going on?

347
00:15:50.640 --> 00:15:53.720
What?! It's rushing straight toward us!

348
00:15:53.720 --> 00:15:57.060
They're really gonna launch
onto the main island!

349
00:15:57.060 --> 00:16:01.020
No way! They can't jump over that iron fence!

350
00:16:04.030 --> 00:16:06.320
Get a move on! Don't let them charge in!

351
00:16:06.950 --> 00:16:08.950
Close the gate!

352
00:16:19.370 --> 00:16:20.630
Hey, granny!

353
00:16:20.630 --> 00:16:22.040
Huh? What's up?

354
00:16:22.040 --> 00:16:23.590
Change of plans!

355
00:16:23.590 --> 00:16:26.130
Guys, looks like we're changing our plan.

356
00:16:26.130 --> 00:16:30.340
The samurai man says everyone
needs to hold on tight to something.

357
00:16:30.340 --> 00:16:32.550
"Hold on tight"?!

358
00:16:32.550 --> 00:16:35.560
Hey, Swordsmoron! What's the big idea?!

359
00:16:35.560 --> 00:16:38.480
They closed the main gate.

360
00:16:38.480 --> 00:16:40.020
They what?!

361
00:16:40.020 --> 00:16:42.810
What?! This is terrible!
We're gonna crash into the gate!

362
00:16:42.810 --> 00:16:44.440
What'll we do?! What'll we do?!

363
00:16:44.440 --> 00:16:46.940
Break away, Kokoro!

364
00:16:45.030 --> 00:16:46.940
What'll we do?! What'll we do?!

365
00:16:48.570 --> 00:16:50.320
Don't worry.

366
00:16:50.320 --> 00:16:51.490
There's a way.

367
00:16:56.750 --> 00:16:58.710
Push that fence, frog!

368
00:16:58.710 --> 00:17:00.580
– What?!
– What?!

369
00:17:25.770 --> 00:17:27.150
He can't...!

370
00:17:27.150 --> 00:17:30.200
Any farther and we'll
run aground on the iron fence!

371
00:17:39.080 --> 00:17:41.540
No way!

372
00:17:42.170 --> 00:17:43.670
The sea train...

373
00:17:43.670 --> 00:17:46.000
...is flying!

374
00:17:46.000 --> 00:17:49.010
No! We're gonna die!

375
00:17:49.010 --> 00:17:51.510
What?! We're gonna die?!

376
00:17:52.760 --> 00:17:55.430
Nami, hurry into my arms!

377
00:17:55.430 --> 00:17:58.470
We're gonna land in that gaping hole, you idiot!

378
00:18:03.020 --> 00:18:06.820
Zoro! You've figured out our landing, right?!

379
00:18:09.530 --> 00:18:11.030
Just leave it to...

380
00:18:19.290 --> 00:18:20.120
luck.

381
00:18:20.950 --> 00:18:23.170
– It's up to luck?!
– It's up to luck?!

382
00:18:30.050 --> 00:18:31.760
Oimo is down!

383
00:18:50.110 --> 00:18:53.200
A-Are you... the Straw Hats?!

384
00:18:53.200 --> 00:18:54.200
That's right!

385
00:18:54.200 --> 00:18:55.450
– We are?!
– We are?!

386
00:18:56.200 --> 00:18:59.660
Whatever. It doesn't matter.

387
00:18:59.660 --> 00:19:01.410
C'mon, shake a leg!

388
00:19:01.410 --> 00:19:06.580
All right, guys! Press on as far as we can go!

389
00:19:06.580 --> 00:19:09.040
– Yeah!
– Yeah!

390
00:19:19.050 --> 00:19:20.600
Paulie!

391
00:19:21.220 --> 00:19:22.140
Dammit!

392
00:19:23.560 --> 00:19:25.560
Who the hell are you?!

393
00:19:25.940 --> 00:19:28.690
We're Enies Lobby's elite guards,

394
00:19:28.690 --> 00:19:32.320
the Watchdogs of the Law,
Watchdogs for short!

395
00:19:32.320 --> 00:19:36.030
Watchdogs of the Law
Elite Guards of Enies Lobby

396
00:19:33.110 --> 00:19:36.030
Under orders from Chief Justice Baskerville,

397
00:19:36.030 --> 00:19:39.320
we'll cast judgment on you
and bring you down at this gate!

398
00:19:40.200 --> 00:19:43.950
Dammit! They send one guard
after another to block us!

399
00:19:44.330 --> 00:19:46.620
Oimo! What're you doing?!

400
00:19:46.620 --> 00:19:50.130
How could you let
pirates like them open the gate?!

401
00:19:50.130 --> 00:19:50.750
Ow!

402
00:19:54.260 --> 00:19:55.880
Oimo passed out!

403
00:19:57.840 --> 00:20:00.760
– Not good! He's up and at 'em!
– Not good! He's up and at 'em!

404
00:20:03.720 --> 00:20:05.600
Oimo won't forgive you!

405
00:20:05.600 --> 00:20:08.480
You're not gonna get away with this!

406
00:20:15.990 --> 00:20:17.950
– What?!
– What?!

407
00:20:33.800 --> 00:20:38.090
Wh-Why the hell did Rocketman...
come from the sky?!

408
00:20:38.090 --> 00:20:41.010
– Opening the gates was pointless?!
– Opening the gates was pointless?!

409
00:20:49.390 --> 00:20:51.770
Wh-What just happened?!

410
00:20:52.480 --> 00:20:55.940
Do you think they're okay
after crashing in like that?

411
00:21:01.780 --> 00:21:03.870
Th-They aren't coming out...

412
00:21:20.050 --> 00:21:22.010
Hey, what happened?!

413
00:21:25.390 --> 00:21:28.100
Wh-Who are those two?!

414
00:21:35.070 --> 00:21:36.360
Huh?

415
00:21:37.070 --> 00:21:39.110
Should we have introduced ourselves?

416
00:21:39.610 --> 00:21:42.110
That's stupid. Why should we have?

417
00:21:42.110 --> 00:21:44.030
It's Roronoa's group!

418
00:21:44.030 --> 00:21:46.240
– It's about time!
– It's about time!

419
00:21:51.750 --> 00:21:54.040
All according to plan...

420
00:21:54.040 --> 00:21:55.500
Really?!
